imdb.plot outline: Teen Talk with Hannah is a new kind of talk show. It is written for teens, and presented by a teen. Teen Talk will not only cover all the topics you'd expect in a show for teens, from fashion to DIY to school, it will also tackle the tough topics like bullying, human trafficking, drinking and drugs and the other topics that teens are dealing with. Written and produced with a unique angle, Teen Talk with Hannah definitely delivers.
imdb.title: Teen Talk with Hannah
plot: Positive talk show highlighting information for teens, the community and parents.::Tracy Hoobyar
